00:28:08,938 --> 00:28:10,940
-Wait, I will call.
-Oh, hello!

506
00:28:11,315 --> 00:28:12,525
Where are you going?

507
00:28:12,608 --> 00:28:15,403
The gas is poisonous!
Get out of here.

508
00:28:15,486 --> 00:28:18,406
