535
00:30:36,210 --> 00:30:39,004
-I've brought you--
-Mom, look at this!

536
00:30:39,088 --> 00:30:41,757
Thanks to you,
I look like a hermit.

537
00:30:41,840 --> 00:30:43,092
Put this on.

538
00:30:44,343 --> 00:30:46,220
-Right.
-Okay.

539
00:30:46,345 --> 00:30:47,596
And take this.

540
00:30:48,013 --> 00:30:49,348
-What's this?
-The prasad.

541
00:30:49,431 --> 00:30:50,724
Listen.

542
00:30:51,517 --> 00:30:53,686
Don't give it to anybody else.

543
00:30:54,311 --> 00:30:56,480
You need more protection
than anyone else.

544
00:30:56,564 --> 00:30:58,190
I always have a bomb
in my pocket, don't I?

545
00:30:58,274 --> 00:30:59,692
You're impossible.

546
00:30:59,817 --> 00:31:01,151
What's cooking?

547
00:31:01,235 --> 00:31:02,903
I'm not staging a
performance here!

548
00:31:02,987 --> 00:31:04,488
Why are you guys here?
I don't need any help.

549
00:31:04,572 --> 00:31:06,407
You just want to steal
my recipe, don't you?

550
00:31:06,490 --> 00:31:08,576
-Go on, leave.
-May I say something?

551
00:31:09,076 --> 00:31:10,744
You look very fit.

552
00:31:11,161 --> 00:31:13,539
-You look like his younger brother!
-Did you hear that?

553
00:31:13,706 --> 00:31:15,791
